### Get logs for a user
GET {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}:{{$dotenv PORT}}/logs?userId={{$dotenv USER_UUID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_TOKEN}}

### Mark a log as complete
PATCH {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}:{{$dotenv PORT}}/logs/{{$dotenv LOG_ID}}/done
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_TOKEN}}

### Missing token (should return 401)
GET {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}:{{$dotenv PORT}}/logs?userId=<paste-user-uuid-here>

### Invalid token (should return 403)
GET {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}:{{$dotenv PORT}}/logs?userId=<paste-user-uuid-here>
Authorization: Bearer wrong-token

### Invalid userId — not a UUID (should return 400)
GET {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}:{{$dotenv PORT}}/logs?userId=not-a-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_TOKEN}}

### Invalid log id — not a UUID (should return 400)
PATCH {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}:{{$dotenv PORT}}/logs/not-a-uuid/done
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_TOKEN}}
